venue.address_1: 1245 Worcester Rd. Natick. Inside the Natick Collection, between Sears and Nordstrom
venue.name: Finale

item.description: Join us at Finale as we hang out, relax and enjoy great dessert! Everyone pays for their own food/drink. This is going to be a great night- Finale is known for its awesome chocolate desserts!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo), I'll be wearing a green coat. If you need help finding us, call 774 232 0000.
item.why: Come and check out Finale's new location in the Natick Collection. Relax, meet new, friendly and interesting people who live/work in the Metro West area and eat terrific desserts- what a perfect evening!
item.name: Dessert Night at Finale in Natick Collection
